The type of each argument must agree with the type of the corresponding
parameter, except where the standard type coercion, [section 10.6.13](arrays.html#standard-type-coercion "10.6.13 Standard Type Coercion ‣ 10.6 Scalar, Vector, Matrix, and Array Operator Functions ‣ Chapter 10 Arrays ‣ Modelica® Language Specification version 3.6"), can be used to make
